title: RNSB Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for Junior Executive (Trainee) Posts
description: The Rajkot Nagarik Sahakari Bank Limited (RNSB) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 01 Junior Executive (Trainee) Posts. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their Any Degree and Post-graduation can apply for the RNSB Recruitment 2025 . The interested applicants can apply in online mode.
